name: HELL-O (Frogrammer)
description:
Made in a Week for OperaGX Jam with theme - UFO

Fast-paced Highscore Wave survival game

SAFE-Protocol identified you as Unknown Flying Object and you were marked as possible danger from space. Locked in malicious room of machines, you have no option but try to survive as long as you can.

- P1 CONTROLS:

[A/D] - SPIN

[W] - DASH

- P2 CONTROLS:

[LEFT/RIGHT] - SPIN

[UP] - DASH

Made by:

ms_frogrammer - Coding, Level Design, Art

Crase - Animations, Design

Bibiki - SFX, Music
